{"tid":1906601,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(嶺南衡怡紀念中學嘅請入) 麥肇輝老師生前一件鮮為人知嘅事，同97前支香港旗有關","createTime":"2020-03-02T05:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T03:43:07.000Z","uid":52429,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f18b03df0c2ba222d027d9a5a2209b7e8b6ccf35","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"當年Mr. Mak教我班綜合人文科<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pTursno.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTursno.jpg&h=ec519116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說2007年, 當年差唔多接近香港淪陷10週年之際<br />\n有堂佢突然同D學生講起1996年亞特蘭大奧運李麗珊代表香港攞奧運金牌嘅事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xxs1giP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxs1giP.jpg&h=8df6d272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就問D學生:「你地有冇見過以前香港支旗? 回歸之前嗰支呢，藍色上面有支米字旗嗰支」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8S84d6B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8S84d6B.png&h=60e51d5d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當然好多人都冇見過, 當年99.9%中學生都只係知道香港區旗兼認自己係中国人 (嚴俊能都認自己係中国人啦)<br />\n跟住Mr. Mak就同學生講解97前嗰支香港旗同埋旗上面嗰個香港紋章嘅意思<br />\n嗰堂我真係聽得好投入<br />\nMr. Mak, 多謝你令我早幾十年認識香港旗<br />\n雖然你係一個小器鬼, 但係你呢堂對我講影響深遠<br />\n而家諗返起<br />\n我都認為你係罪不至死"},{"pid":"0f37cb852c3a8e0fcf3efe23aee477835a5666f0","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b353ff1a7146d786c9b9afcf9012f9f5c4fc65e3","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8effb5bfc7dfecfc7ca0a0665e7852c99523b993","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832c9dca703cf46a0ce27540cb4c22eace9a411b","tid":1906601,"uid":306681,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d95269574edab615084170dfe087d290b094d7e2","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00372d671819ec312eaf88ab316adf8299ef271a","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a096b5747656e463bffdaca20cfccddc4ab5be6","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e568706b12406e335418619066519bfae859339","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4d3af4742268b84663e953a80f53e75e55ff71","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e8a07c6ec2a780dd619cc51be1b8f24b1859ef","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c6caacf3b6b052c9620523b3c2dbef4084d3b1","tid":1906601,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a449b205f584cd48b44bc4502ef9e73bcd1405e","tid":1906601,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"雖然你係一個小氣鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face